&gt;&gt; Carl Hiaasen: My guitar playing?

00:25:01.180 --> 00:25:02.480
&gt;&gt; Yes.

00:25:02.480 --> 00:25:03.780
&gt;&gt; Carl Hiaasen: Oh, you've
gone right into the -- yeah.

