It's just, I'm obviously
not a well person.

00:27:00.210 --> 00:27:01.880
And these things happen.

00:27:01.880 --> 00:27:03.270
I scream and yell a little bit.

00:27:03.270 --> 00:27:05.230
And then sometimes
