00:27:05.230 --> 00:27:06.600
But thank you for asking.

00:27:06.600 --> 00:27:07.900
Yes.

00:27:07.900 --> 00:27:09.720
&gt;&gt; Right. Skink.

00:27:09.720 --> 00:27:13.290
Was he patterned after a
particular governor of Florida?

00:27:13.290 --> 00:27:14.590
All of them?

00:27:14.590 --> 00:27:18.410
