Florida and referred to Skink?

00:27:18.410 --> 00:27:19.710
&gt;&gt; Carl Hiaasen: Yeah.

00:27:19.710 --> 00:27:21.010
I mean, he wasn't --
Skink was this old,

00:27:21.010 --> 00:27:23.540
and he's been in a
bunch of my novels.

00:27:23.540 --> 00:27:26.520
And he at one time had
been a Vietnam War hero.

00:27:26.520 --> 00:27:27.820
Come home.

00:27:27.820 --> 00:27:29.120
Persuaded to run for governor.

00:27:29.120 --> 00:27:32.530
He gets to Tallahassee, discovers
he's like the only honest human

00:27:32.530 --> 00:27:35.220
in the entire area code of
that part of the panhandle.

00:27:35.220 --> 00:27:37.800
He goes crazy one day,
rips off his clothes,

00:27:37.800 --> 00:27:41.650
runs into the woods
and lives on road kill.

00:27:41.650 --> 00:27:44.610
All seemed like a normal
reaction to Tallahassee.

00:27:44.610 --> 00:27:46.670
If you've ever been
there, and I can tell you.

00:27:46.670 --> 00:27:48.750
But he wasn't modeled --
to answer your question,

00:27:48.750 --> 00:27:50.860
he wasn't modeled on
any real governor.

00:27:50.860 --> 00:27:55.290
But I know of a couple former
governors who would tell people --

00:27:55.290 --> 00:27:59.320
and I met a couple of them -- but
who would tell people that they --

00:27:59.320 --> 00:28:03.820
that I modeled Skink on
them, which was so bizarre.

00:28:03.820 --> 00:28:07.480
I mean, they were so detached
from reality, these guys.

00:28:07.480 --> 00:28:10.080
No. It was one of those
characters you invent

00:28:10.080 --> 00:28:12.790
because you wish there
had been someone like him.

00:28:12.790 --> 00:28:14.420
Florida would be better
off if there were.

00:28:14.420 --> 00:28:18.680
And there is to this day people
who print up bumper stickers

00:28:18.680 --> 00:28:20.220
down there saying "Reelect Skink."

00:28:20.220 --> 00:28:21.760
And they send me pictures of it.

00:28:21.760 --> 00:28:23.060
So that's pretty cool.

00:28:23.060 --> 00:28:24.760
&gt;&gt; And I think you've
answered this question.

00:28:24.760 --> 00:28:29.620
Could you have set your books, say,
