00:28:31.070 --> 00:28:33.270
&gt;&gt; Carl Hiaasen: They certainly
have weirdness in every state.

00:28:33.270 --> 00:28:34.990
I do get the correspondence.

00:28:34.990 --> 00:28:38.410
But I don't think they have -- I
refer to Florida as this great,

00:28:38.410 --> 00:28:40.430
